It will stop producing new messages, but it should read all pending messages. This is what I emulate using:
pipeline().fireUserEventTriggered(ChannelInputShutdownEvent.INSTANCE);
super.flushInbound();
pipeline().fireUserEventTriggered(ChannelInputShutdownReadComplete.INSTANCE);
After that, I make sure that it can not produce more messages discarding any following attempts to write inbound.

